\n            .izushi-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr) !important; }\n        }\n        @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n            .izushi-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }\n            .izushi-main-title h2 { font-size: 2.5rem !important; }\n            .stat-card { padding: 35px 20px !important; }\n            .count { font-size: 2.6rem !important; }\n            .yukyu-label { font-size: 0.7rem !important; }\n        }\n        \n        .stat-card { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); transition: all 0.8s ease-out; }\n        .is-visible { opacity: 1 !important; transform: translateY(0) !important; }\n        .count { visibility: hidden; }\n        .is-visible .count { visibility: visible; }\n    </style>\n\n    <div style=\"max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px;\">\n        <div class=\"izushi-main-title\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 60px;\">\n            <h2 style=\"font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: #003366; margin: 0;\">Numbers</h2>\n            <p style=\"font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #0050a0; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.3em; margin-top: 5px; text-transform: uppercase;\">DATA OF IZUSHI</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; margin: 60px 0 30px;\">\n            <h3 style=\"font-size: 1.6rem; color: #003366; margin: 0; padding-right: 20px; font-weight: 700;\">会社規模・歴史</h3>\n            <div style=\"height: 1px; background: #d1d9e6; flex-grow: 1;\"></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"izushi-grid\" style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px;\">\n            <div class=\"stat-card\" style=\"background: #ffffff; padding: 40px 25px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.05); text-align: center;\">\n                <span style=\"display: block; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 15px; color: #003366;\">創業</span>\n                <div style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\"><span class=\"count\" style=\"font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 3.8rem; font-weight: 800; color: #003366; line-height: 1;\" data-target=\"1910\">0</span><span style=\"font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-left: 5px;\">年</span></div>\n                <span style=\"font-size: 0.9rem; color: #0050a0; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.5; display: block;\">100年を超える歴史は<br>確かな信頼と安定の証です</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"stat-card\" style=\"background: #ffffff; padding: 40px 25px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.05); text-align: center;\">\n                <span style=\"display: block; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 15px; color: #003366;\">国内拠点</span>\n                <div style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\"><span class=\"count\" style=\"font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 3.8rem; font-weight: 800; color: #003366; line-height: 1;\" data-target=\"12\">0</span><span style=\"font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-left: 5px;\">拠点</span></div>\n                <span style=\"font-size: 0.9rem; color: #0050a0; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.5; display: block;\">全国主要都市を網羅し<br>迅速なサポート体制を構築</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"stat-card\" style=\"background: #ffffff; padding: 40px 25px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.05); text-align: center;\">\n                <span style=\"display: block; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 15px; color: #003366;\">展示会出展数</span>\n                <div style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\"><span class=\"count\" style=\"font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 3.8rem; font-weight: 800; color: #003366; line-height: 1;\" data-target=\"6\">0</span><span style=\"font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-left: 5px;\">回/年</span></div>\n                <span style=\"font-size: 0.9rem; color: #0050a0; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.5; display: block;\">2025年実績 6回！<br>最新の市場ニーズを常にキャッチ</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"stat-card\" style=\"background: #ffffff; padding: 40px 25px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.05); text-align: center;\">\n                <span style=\"display: block; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 15px; color: #003366;\">PBブランド数</span>\n                <div style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\"><span class=\"count\" style=\"font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 3.8rem; font-weight: 800; color: #003366; line-height: 1;\" data-target=\"21\">0</span><span style=\"font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-left: 5px;\">種</span></div>\n                <span style=\"font-size: 0.9rem; color: #0050a0; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.5; display: block;\">商社の枠を超えたメーカー機能で<br>高付加価値を提供しています</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"stat-card\" style=\"background: #ffffff; padding: 40px 25px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.05); text-align: center;\">\n                <span style=\"display: block; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 15px; color: #003366;\">海外取引メーカー数</span>\n                <div style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\"><span class=\"count\" style=\"font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 3.8rem; font-weight: 800; color: #003366; line-height: 1;\" data-target=\"16\">0</span><span style=\"font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-left: 5px;\">社</span></div>\n                <span style=\"font-size: 0.9rem; color: #0050a0; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.5; display: block;\">世界最先端の技術を日本へ。<br>グローバルな視野を養えます</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"stat-card\" style=\"background: #ffffff; padding: 40px 25px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.05); text-align: center;\">\n                <span style=\"display: block; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 15px; color: #003366;\">連続黒字経営</span>\n                <div style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\"><span class=\"count\" style=\"font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 3.8rem; font-weight: 800; color: #003366; line-height: 1;\" data-target=\"16\">0</span><span style=\"font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-left: 5px;\">年</span></div>\n                <span style=\"font-size: 0.9rem; color: #0050a0; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.5; display: block;\">リーマンショック後も継続。<br>安心して長く働ける経営基盤です</span>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; margin: 60px 0 30px;\">\n            <h3 style=\"font-size: 1.6rem; color: #003366; margin: 0; padding-right: 20px; font-weight: 700;\">社員構成・多様性</h3>\n            <div style=\"height: 1px; background: #d1d9e6; flex-grow: 1;\"></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"izushi-grid\" style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px;\">\n            <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px;\">\n                <div class=\"stat-card\" style=\"background: #ffffff; padding: 30px 25px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.05); text-align: center; flex: 1;\">\n                    <span style=\"display: block; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #003366;\">従業員数</span>\n                    <div><span class=\"count\" style=\"font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: #003366; line-height: 1;\" data-target=\"121\">0</span><span style=\"font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-left: 5px;\">名</span></div>\n                    <div style=\"margin-top: 10px; background: #003366; color: #fff; padding: 6px 15px; border-radius: 20px; display: inline-block; font-weight: 800; font-size: 1rem;\">平均年齢 <span class=\"count\" data-target=\"41\" style=\"font-family: 'Montserrat';\">0</span>歳</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"stat-card\" style=\"background: #ffffff; padding: 30px 25px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.05); text-align: center; flex: 1;\">\n                    <span style=\"display: block; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #003366;\">平均勤続年数</span>\n                    <div><span class=\"count\" style=\"font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: #003366; line-height: 1;\" data-target=\"12\">0</span><span style=\"font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-left: 5px;\">年</span></div>\n                    <div style=\"margin-top: 10px; color: #003366; font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.1rem; border: 2px solid #003366; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block;\">最長勤続 <span class=\"count\" data-target=\"44\" style=\"font-family: 'Montserrat';\">0</span>年</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"stat-card\" style=\"background: #ffffff; padding: 30px 25px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.05); text-align: center;\">\n                <span style=\"display: block; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #003366;\">年齢構成</span>\n                <div style=\"background: #fdfdfe; border: 1px solid #edf2f7; border-radius: 10px; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; text-align: left;\">\n                    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\"><div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 2px; color: #003366;\"><span>20代</span><span>24.8%</span></div><div style=\"height: 10px; background: #f0f0f0; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden;\"><div class=\"bar-fill\" style=\"height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #5a9bd5, #003366); width: 0;\" data-width=\"24.8%\"></div></div></div>\n                    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\"><div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bott